Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:36.50,OP - CN,Shadow,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\bord0.5\blur10}也许 这是一场无果的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:36.50,OP - JP,Shadow,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\bord0.5\blur10}たぶん実らない恋かもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.71,OP - CN,Shadow,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\bord0.5\blur10}也是一段难以言喻的爱情
